button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iey1665703199519.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iey1665703199519.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iey1665703199519.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iey1665703199519\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface logical for setting options for the Java Virtual Machine used in XSLT transformations.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"iey1665703199519__topic_d137900e1_d137901e1_d137902e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iey1665703199519__p_d137903e1_d137904e1_d137905e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">JVM_OPTIONS</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> } <var class=\"keyword varname\">Switch</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iey1665703199519__p_d137906e1_d137907e1_d137908e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">JVM_OPTIONS</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> }<code class=\"ph codeph\">-Xmx<var class=\"keyword varname\">MaxMemorySize</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iey1665703199519__section_owt_zw2_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d478242e80\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"iey1665703199519__ul_szj_2x2_vvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iey1665703199519__li_d48584e1_d48585e1_d48586e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Switch</var>—valid Java option; for details see Java documentation. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iey1665703199519__li_d48587e1_d48588e1_d48589e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-Xmx<var class=\"keyword varname\">MaxMemorySize</var>\n</code>—maximum Java heap size; valid values depend on the specifications of the\n               machine. For example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">-Xmx256m</code> allocates a maximum of 256 MB of\n               memory. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iey1665703199519__section_e2h_bx2_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d478242e107\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iey1665703199519__table_w1680ab1b5b5b3_w1681ab1b5b5_w1682ab1b5_w1683ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Assignment file: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Application </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vcm1665702739978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vcm1665702739978.html\" title=\"Use the [LOGICALS] section of the assignment file to assign values to logicals that can be accessed using the $logical ProcScript function. Each application can have its own set of logicals.\">[LOGICALS]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> none </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iey1665703199519__section_azw_cx2_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d478242e163\">Description</h2>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"iey1665703199519__note_tlq_jx2_vvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Java switches are case-sensitive, so ensure that\n            any switch is correctly set.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iey1665703199519__p_d137918e1_d137919e1_d137920e1\">If you run out of memory when using the XSLT\n            component API, you can set the <code class=\"ph codeph\">-Xmx</code> option to increase the amount of\n            memory available to Java.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iey1665703199519__section_bmr_gz4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d478242e178\">Example</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"iey1665703199519__pre_mxc_lx2_vvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[LOGICALS]\nJVM_OPTIONS = -Xmx512m</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ria1665702906209.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>XMLTRANSFORM</a><p>Transform an XML stream using an XSLT style sheet.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528513\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528513\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "JVM_OPTIONS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface logical for setting options for the Java Virtual Machine used in XSLT transformations. JVM_OPTIONS { = } Switch JVM_OPTIONS { = } -Xmx MaxMemorySize Arguments Switch —valid Java option; for details see Java documentation. -Xmx MaxMemorySize —maximum Java heap size; valid values depend on the specifications of the machine. For example, -Xmx256m allocates a maximum of 256 MB of memory. Defaults Assignment file: Application Section: [LOGICALS] Default value: none Description Note: Java switches are case-sensitive, so ensure that any switch is correctly set. If you run out of memory when using the XSLT component API, you can set the -Xmx option to increase the amount of memory available to Java. Example [LOGICALS] JVM_OPTIONS = -Xmx512m Copy Related Links XMLTRANSFORM Transform an XML stream using an XSLT style sheet. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}